    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make GCSE Maths optional and introduce an alternative, easier qualification",
        "additional_details": "Many people struggle with numbers, and the requirement to pass GCSE Maths puts them under pressure. This can cause stress and anxiety.",
        "background": "I want to introduce an alternative, easier maths qualification for people for whom GCSE Maths isn\u2019t attainable. This qualification could have different requirements that are more achievable.",
